1.0.name: wordpress/ampachenowplaying
1.0.description: The Ampache Now Playing wordpress plugin displays information about the current playing song on an Ampache server on wordpress. The information is loaded with jQuery/Ajax which is beneficial if the Ampache server in question has a slow connection or is run on old hardware.
